<td align="center"><b>
<i>Hesperapis fuchsi</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Viereck, 1909&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Panurgomia fuchsi </i>Viereck, 1909; <i>Hesperapis nitidulus </i>Cockerell, 1916, synonymy of Stage, unpublished dissertation; <i>Hesperapis nitidula </i>Cockerell, 1916, corrected termination; <i>Hesperapis semirudis </i>Cockerell, 1910, synonymy of Stage, unpublished dissertation; <i>Hesperapis wilmattae </i>Cockerell, 1933, synonymy of Stage, unpublished dissertation</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
